{"id": 709, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于减肥，你又自欺欺人了一整年吗？", "description": "减肥减了一年，成功胖了八斤。（题图来自：maori sakai）", "record_count": 3424, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183606RPebAXJ5lQ9uGZtc.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-12-20T01:09:52Z", "options": [{"id": 35584, "content": "我要多吃点蔬菜减减肥！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 325422}, {"id": 35585, "content": "减肥什么的，说出来只不过是为了吓吓肥头的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 180644}, {"id": 35586, "content": "当一个人孤独的时候心才会沉静下来，然后才能不怎么想念食物", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 271922}, {"id": 35588, "content": "亲身验证越减越肥?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256814}, {"id": 35589, "content": "男的 想健康增肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246331}, {"id": 41477, "content": "就你话多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416583}, {"id": 35590, "content": "瘦不下来的原因是自拍P完还是美的", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245547}, {"id": 35591, "content": "2015无缘瘦下来?    2016一定再战!?", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372530}, {"id": 35847, "content": "天冷就不想动", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360292}, {"id": 36872, "content": "Ch ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 385619}, {"id": 35597, "content": "越想瘦 越容易胖 你不去想了   倒瘦下来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 327448}, {"id": 35598, "content": "五月底开始坚持健身房，当时体重59，健身期间到过60，现在56 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 362708}, {"id": 35599, "content": "160公分，42公斤。还每天嚷着要减肥。白眼都快淹死我了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219212}, {"id": 35855, "content": "中午少吃了二块肉，到了晚上对自己说：中午那么辛苦，犒劳一下自己吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228492}, {"id": 35601, "content": "心宽体胖。无法让自己成个小心眼来减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372544}, {"id": 37905, "content": "周一到周五轻断食。却在周六日暴饮暴食", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 264683}, {"id": 36882, "content": "想做兼职的加qq497839917，有手机有wifi就可以做任务了，在家或者单位都可以做，轻松赚取零花钱，做的好还可以当主要经济收入呢，仅限苹果手机用户。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 385774}, {"id": 35603, "content": "我最骄傲的事就是怎么吃都不胖哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91804}, {"id": 36115, "content": "神魔的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 377671}, {"id": 35604, "content": "一周瘦了12斤。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 36884, "content": "说到减肥  就想到运动  说到运动  就想躺在床上不想动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 385806}, {"id": 38676, "content": "87公斤到68公斤", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 350213}, {"id": 35605, "content": "买秤之后已经减了10多斤，管好嘴多运动才是正解", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 352748}, {"id": 35862, "content": "只能说，真的好难", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 374500}, {"id": 35608, "content": "不需要减肥啊，暴坐了半年准备减肥时发现并没有什么变化…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236895}, {"id": 36632, "content": "支持。。？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 382705}, {"id": 35610, "content": "我竟然说要寒假过年减肥！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 359688}, {"id": 36380, "content": "永远瘦不了⛈", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211915duKU3Lz1RkAri05Y.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 380575}, {"id": 35613, "content": "不吃好哪有力气减肥？减肥不就是为了更好的吃吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 318563}, {"id": 35870, "content": "过胖而短暂的人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354268}, {"id": 37919, "content": "虽然没有达到自己想要的目标，不过半年内还是瘦了18斤，明年一定要瘦到100斤??????", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273278}, {"id": 35617, "content": "我一定会瘦下来 而且瘦下来一定是个美女", "image": null, "praise_count": 98, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265887}, {"id": 35619, "content": "总是很负责的对自己说这是最后一餐....之后又一餐......", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372799}, {"id": 35621, "content": "上半年瘦十斤，下半年长二十", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372848}, {"id": 36133, "content": "不吃晚饭，多跑步。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 377337}, {"id": 35622, "content": "管住嘴 迈开腿 so easy??", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294948}, {"id": 35623, "content": "一年不变?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292692}, {"id": 36136, "content": "冬天吃了 夏天在减", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211909OwRtvZl7Ixdh3Nq1.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 377541}, {"id": 35881, "content": "减了八斤胖了十斤", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 375310}, {"id": 40237, "content": "怎莫吃都胖不了——因为我是一根苗条的线", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 415633}, {"id": 37934, "content": "每次都安慰自己，吃一点没关系。。。饿肚子做不了运动啊。。。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287661}, {"id": 35631, "content": "喊了一年减肥。残酷的是年底重了6公斤！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209182}, {"id": 35889, "content": "减的营养不良了都没瘦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260010}, {"id": 35634, "content": "说要增肥已经说了好几年了，到现在还没胖起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253533}, {"id": 35636, "content": "77kg to60kg", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335814}, {"id": 35892, "content": "全身能瘦下来后就像整了容一样 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 375429}, {"id": 38965, "content": "我瘦过啊，那个时候168cm，51kg，Ccup，结果期末压力一大。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403287}, {"id": 36663, "content": "去青藏高原，疯跑一阵，高反一次，送医抢救，绝壁让你三天瘦11市斤～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122292}, {"id": 37176, "content": "总是以，要好好享受美食为借口", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 384972}, {"id": 36409, "content": "每天说明天再少吃点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 315558}]}